See README.stoney for the original README.

This is a revised version of the original c2man code by Graham Stoney.

The following changes have been made:

* Configuration is now done via GNU autotools
* Amiga, VMS, PC, NEXT, and Apollo support has been removed
* The code has been ansified.
* Some bugs have been fixed
* The parser recognizes some GCC'isms
* Some code has been incorporated from Debian Patches; see ChangeLog
* No longer relevent sections of the FAQ have been removed; the original is in FAQ.stoney
* ChangeLog now provides changes since 2.0.41; see CHANGES & ChangeLog.stoney for older changes

